Class CaseBaseFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jLOAF.preprocessing.filter.CaseBaseFilter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActionClustering, Clustering, FeatureSelectionAlgorithm, NoFilter, Sampling, Standardization, UnderSampling, WeightsSeperatorFilter

    public abstract class CaseBaseFilter
extends java.lang.Object
    a caseBase Filter is the parent class of many casebase filter, they all use the decorator pattern , where a casebase filter takes a casebase filter which also takes another casebase filter, and so on.
